secondary_street_name: Rear of 73-103 Gillespie Road, at land 117-119 Gillespie Road; and land at 133-139 Highbury Hill
description:
Redesign of the Highbury Stadium site redevelopment as approved full and outline planning permission under ref. P00/2501 on 30 May 2002.  The revised scheme now comprises of 711 residential units with provision for a general medical practitioners' surgery (Class D1), a nursery (Class D1), a gym/health club (Class D2) and a retail unit (Class A1) along with associated areas of parking and landscaping.  (A Listed Building Consent application ref. P05/0451 has also been submitted in respect of the East Stand).
PLEASE NOTE THAT THE CONSULTATION EXPIRY DATE ON THESE PARTICULAR APPLICATIONS IS 21/04/05.
decision_conditions: This notice was not produced from APAS therefore the conditions were not input. They are available in Documentum (DIP)
